description: This dataset displays all the location of all Target Retail Stores across the USA. The information was collected from Target's website at target.com on 9.17.2008. The data includes information on: Store name, Store location(street address, city, state, zip), Phone Number, and lat/lon coordinates. The lat/lon coordinates were determined by geocoding the street address of the store.
